# Ancient High-Tech Symbol Compression System
# Cursor AI Configuration

## What This Project Is

A deterministic text compression system that encodes words as 1-bit symbols with
template-based positional reconstruction. Built for Hive blockchain deployment.
Target: 5KB on-chain storage with 19.3:1 compression ratio and 100% reconstruction.

## Architecture Philosophy

**Ancient/High-Tech Principle**: Store only tiny codes on-chain. All intelligence
lives in templates (pre-computed lookup tables). The decoder reconstructs everything
from codes + templates with zero ambiguity.

